Steaks hachés pur bœuf spécial burger CARREFOUR LE MARCHE
    2 x 140g
Salade iceberg CARREFOUR LE MARCHE : 350g

2 cheddar per patty

wrap it in foil

---
you can replace with cabbage cooked in water for 1-2 minute

----------
1- 280g mcdo
I used half tsp per 280g
    might need more salt since it's fatty meat ?

sauce: ketchup 
sauce: mustard + mayo mixed 5 to 1

oignons caramélisés + un peu sel
tomate tranches un peu sel

1 tranche cheddar + 1 tranche emmental

from top to bottom : sauces oignon 2 tranches tomatoes 1 tranches cheddar burger 1 tranche emmental
    1 tomates entiere for the two burgers of 280g

tips : salt meat and Keep it cold
    cook one side until cooked, flip and add cheddar x2
    cook until cooked and put in dish and add emmental immediatly

salt the burger one day in advance

2 salads per burger : fill them with sauce on one side.
    
cook thick burgers @170C and use duck fat before
    used carrefour Steaks hachés pur bœuf spécial burger CARREFOUR LE MARCHE

